(@TGUID+4,'It\'s a strange order, you can\'t deny. Suspicious food? Under that definition, you should arrest Belfast!','0','0','0','1','0','Fras Siabi - say_inn_4'),
(@TGUID+5,'I HEARD THAT! No more ale for you! Not a drop!','0','0','0','5','0','Michael Belfast - say_inn_5'),
